amen.  I agree, we want to use names, and the domain system
doesn't work.  My suggestion is that we start moving to
secondary root servers on every major campus.  We propose to
do that here.  In addition, I think we need to give a lot
more thought to the retransmission characteristics of the
domain system.  Currently, when you make a query on the
Arpanet, you are guarnateed to generate about 10 requests.
This has to be having some effect on the network.

